				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\text{C}}_\beta $$\end{document} lies at a distance less than or equal to the lower boundary are assigned a neighbor weight of 1.0 (i.e., they are counted as complete neighbors), amino acids whose \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
