Neighbor vector (NV) The neighbor vector algorithm is an extension of the neighbor count algorithm that takes into account the spatial orientation of neighboring amino acids.
\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
